data.description: MLS# 271434 Welcome to this great South Kennewick home.  This spacious home offers 2343 square feet with4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and a bonus room!  The open concept layout also offers a high, vaulted ceiling and a dining nook.  The laundry room is located inside the home between the 2-car garage.  This home also offers a covered patio and decent sized yard that won't require a lot to maintain.  Come take a look at what this home has to offer!
